<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cover Letter - {{ candidate_name }}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles/classic.css">
    <style>
        /* Cover Letter Specific Styles */
        .cover-letter {
            line-height: 1.5; /* Slightly more spacing for readability */
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        
        .cover-letter .header h1 {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: left; /* Left-align for cover letters */
            margin-bottom: 4pt;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .contact {
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-bottom: 16pt;
        }
        
        .date-address {
            margin: 16pt 0;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        
        .date-address p {
            margin-bottom: 4pt;
        }
        
        .salutation {
            margin-bottom: 12pt;
        }
        
        .pain-paragraph, .promise-paragraph, .close-paragraph {
            margin-bottom: 12pt;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        
        .signature {
            margin-top: 20pt;
        }
        
        /* Emphasis for key points */
        .emphasis {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .metric {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2C5282;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="cover-letter">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>{{ candidate_name }}</h1>
            <div class="contact">{{ email }}{% if phone %} | {{ phone }}{% endif %}{% if location %} | {{ location }}{% endif %}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="date-address">
            <p>{{ current_date }}</p>
            {% if company_address %}
            <p>{{ hiring_manager_name | default("Hiring Manager") }}<br>
            {{ company_name }}<br>
            {{ company_address }}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        
        <div class="salutation">
            <p>Dear {{ hiring_manager_name | default("Hiring Manager") }},</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Paragraph 1: Hook & Pain Point -->
        <p class="pain-paragraph">
            Seeing {{ company_name }}'s {{ company_challenge_context | default("recent growth and market expansion") }}, 
            I imagine <span class="emphasis">{{ inferred_pain_point | default("scaling operations efficiently while maintaining quality") }}</span> 
            is a top priority. With the {{ job_requirements.industry | default("technology") }} market evolving rapidly, 
            {{ specific_challenge_detail | default("implementing robust systems and processes") }} 
            requires both <span class="emphasis">{{ key_skill_1 | default(core_competency_1) }}</span> expertise and 
            <span class="emphasis">{{ key_skill_2 | default(core_competency_2) }}</span> experience.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Paragraph 2: Bridge & Promise -->
        <p class="promise-paragraph">
            In my previous role at <span class="emphasis">{{ previous_company }}</span>, I 
            <span class="metric">{{ top_quantified_achievement }}</span>, resulting in 
            {{ specific_metric | default("measurable improvements in efficiency and performance") }}. 
            This experience in <span class="emphasis">{{ relevant_skill_area | default(skill_area) }}</span> is directly applicable to 
            {{ connection_to_pain_point | default("addressing similar operational challenges") }}. 
            My expertise in <span class="emphasis">{{ core_competency | default(core_competency_1) }}</span> has consistently delivered 
            {{ success_pattern | default("consistent value delivery") }} for {{ target_audience | default("growing organizations") }}.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Paragraph 3: Close & Call to Action -->
        <p class="close-paragraph">
            I am confident that my experience in <span class="emphasis">{{ primary_skill_area | default(skill_area) }}</span> 
            can deliver similar results for {{ company_name }}. I am eager to discuss how my background in 
            <span class="emphasis">{{ specialization_area | default(core_competency_1) }}</span> can support your team's goals. 
            I look forward to hearing from you.
        </p>
        
        <p class="signature">
            Sincerely,<br><br>
            {{ candidate_name }}
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>